* A Partial set view for a portion of the keys in a MediaFormat object.
     *
     * This class is needed as we want to return a portion of the actual format keys in getKeys()
     * and another portion of the keys in getFeatures(), and still allow the view properties.

methods.name: protected abstract boolean keepKey(String key)
methods.comment: Returns true if this set should include this key

methods.name: protected abstract String mapKeyToItem(String key)
methods.comment: Maps a key from the underlying key set into its new value in this key set

methods.name: protected abstract String mapItemToKey(String item)
methods.comment: Maps a key from this key set into its original value in the underlying key set
